query:
SELECT /* servers.findAll */
                  s.vpn_id
                , v.vpn_name 
                , s.terminal_id 
                , t.terminal_name 
                , t.owner_user_id 
                , s.public_ip 
                , s.created_at 
                  FROM servers s
            INNER JOIN vpns v
                    ON s.vpn_id = v.vpn_id 
            INNER JOIN terminals t 
                    ON s.terminal_id =t.terminal_id 
            INNER JOIN users u
                    ON t.owner_user_id = u.user_id
            ;
